status.description:
Product creation or update status. Product information is processed in queues.
Possible parameter values:
- `pending`—product in the processing queue;
- `imported`—product loaded successfully;
- `failed`—product loaded with errors;
- `skipped`—product wasn't updated because there were no changes in the request.

productv3GetProductListRequestFilterFilt.description:
Filter by product visibility:
  - `ALL`: all products;
  - `VISIBLE`: products visible to customers;
  - `INVISIBLE`: products not visible to customers;
  - `EMPTY_STOCK`: products with no stocks specified;
  - `NOT_MODERATED`: products that didn't pass moderation;
  - `MODERATED`: products that passed moderation;
  - `DISABLED`: products visible to customers but not available for purchase;
  - `STATE_FAILED`: products, which creation ended up with an error;
  - `READY_TO_SUPPLY`: products ready for shipping;
  - `VALIDATION_STATE_PENDING`: products that are being pre-moderated by a validator;
  - `VALIDATION_STATE_FAIL`: products that didn't pass pre-moderation by a validator;
  - `VALIDATION_STATE_SUCCESS`: products that passed pre-moderation by a validator;
  - `TO_SUPPLY`: products ready for sale;
  - `IN_SALE`: products on sale;
  - `REMOVED_FROM_SALE`: products hidden from customers;
  - `OVERPRICED`: overpriced products;
  - `CRITICALLY_OVERPRICED`: critically overpriced products;
  - `EMPTY_BARCODE`: products without a barcode;
  - `BARCODE_EXISTS`: products with a barcode;
  - `QUARANTINE`: products in quarantine after a price change for more than 50%;
  - `ARCHIVED`: archived products;
  - `OVERPRICED_WITH_STOCK`: products on sale with a price higher than other sellers;
  - `PARTIAL_APPROVED`: products on sale with blank or incomplete descriptions.

ErrorErrorLevel.description:
Error level description: 
  - `ERROR_LEVEL_UNSPECIFIED`: not identified;
  - `ERROR_LEVEL_ERROR`: critical error, you can't sell the product;
  - `ERROR_LEVEL_INTERNAL`: critical error, you can't sell the product;
  - `ERROR_LEVEL_WARNING`: non-critical error, you can sell the product.

[Learn more about errors when creating products in the Seller Knowledge Base](https://seller-edu.ozon.ru/work-with-goods/zagruzka-tovarov/creating-goods/oshibki-pri-rabote-s-kartochkami).

