message.description:
Error message:

  - `coordinates not provided`—you didn't pass coordinates;
  - `invalid coordinates, must have two points in coordinate`—there is only longitude or a latitiude in some of the polygon points, both of them are required;
  - `the first and last points in loop must be same`—the first and the last points are not the same (according to the standard geojson rules, the points should match);
  - `non-full loops must have at least 4 unique vertices for polygons`—you passed less than 4 polygon points.

