- `OUT_OF_STOCK`: product is out of stock;
- `BANNED_FOR_AREA`: product is blocked for this area;
- `BANNED_FOR_LEGAL`: product is blocked for legal entities;
- `BANNED`: product is blocked;
- `BANNED_FOR_NOT_PREMIUM`: product is blocked for customers without Premium subscription;
- `DELIVERY_UNAVAILABLE`: delivery is unavailable, for example, couriers are overloaded;
- `BANNED_FOR_INDIVIDUAL`: product is blocked for individuals;
- `INVALID_WEIGHT`: product weight isn't specified;
- `INVALID_MULTIPLICITY`: invalid multiplicity in pieces;
- `NOT_FOUND_POINTS_DARK_STORES`: dark stores aren't found;
- `INVALID_MULTI_WAREHOUSES`: products with different delivery schemes are distributed incorrectly;
- `MIN_PRICE`: split is below the minimum price;
- `OZONE_DELIVERY_UNAVAILABLE`: Ozon delivery is unavailable;
- `RFBS_DELIVERY_UNAVAILABLE`: rFBS delivery is unavailable;
- `HACK_COURIER_TAGS`: delivery method is excluded by priority display rule;
- `NO_SLA`: fulfillment standard is missing;
- `DELIVERY_VARIANT_IS_CLOSING`: delivery method has unsuitable status;
- `TPL_NOT_INTEGRATED`: points with unavailable returns;
- `NOT_ALL_WAREHOUSES_ARE_SERVED`: delivery from source warehouse is unavailable;
- `DELIVERY_SLOTS_NOT_FOUND`: time slots aren't found;
- `NO_ROUTE`: route isn't found;
- `CAPACITY_LIMIT`: time slots removed due to capacity limit;
- `PACKAGE_MAX_VOLUME_WEIGHT_RESTRICTION`: restriction of the maximum volume weight of the parcel;
- `PACKAGE_MAX_WEIGHT_RESTRICTION`: restriction of the maximum physical weight of the parcel displayed in kilograms with accuracy to thousandths of a gram;
- `MAX_COST_RESTRICTION`: restriction of the maximum order cost, includes product price and delivery cost, but excludes insurance fee in RUB;
- `MIN_PACKAGE_WEIGHT_RESTRICTION`: restriction of the minimum physical weight of the parcel displayed in kilograms with accuracy to thousandths of a gram;
- `MIN_COST_RESTRICTION`: restriction of the minimum product price for the order in RUB;
- `MAX_DIMENSIONS_RESTRICTION`: restriction of the maximum parcel dimensions in centimeters;
- `PRODUCT_TYPES_RESTRICTION`: restriction on allowed product categories in the order;
- `PRODUCT_TAGS_RESTRICTION`: restriction on allowed product tags in the order;
- `SELECTED_DELIVERY_METHOD_UNAVAILABLE`: selected delivery method became unavailable;
- `SELECTED_DELIVERY_TIMESLOT_UNAVAILABLE`: selected time slot became unavailable;
- `MARKETPLACE_UNAVAILABLE`: order contains products from multiple marketplaces, it can be placed from one marketplace only;
- `INVALID_PVZ_FOR_KGT`: selected pick-up point isn't suitable for bulky products;
- `LEGAL_USER_PREMIUM_SPLIT`: legal entities can't purchase Premium subscription;
- `USER_ALREADY_HAS_PREMIUM`: user already has a Premium subscription and it's not a gift;
- `WAIT_FOR_PAY_SUBSCRIPTION`: user purchased a premium subscription but hasn't paid for the order or the subscription isn't active yet;
- `ADDRESS_NOT_SET`: address isn't set;
- `PICKUP_POINT_DISABLED`: pick-up point is disabled;
- `LEGAL_PREORDER`: pre-order is unavailable for legal entities;
- `DELIVERY_TYPE_FOR_PREORDER`: delivery type is unavailable for pre-order;
- `CROSS_BORDER_PICKUP`: cross-border products can't be delivered to pick-up points;
- `ORDER_CUSTOMS_TYPES`: restrictions on customs types;
- `PACKAGE_MAX_COST`: restriction of maximum package cost, includes product price and delivery cost;
- `SUPER_ECONOM`: Super Economy is unavailable;
- `ECONOM_NOT_FULL_QUANT`: incomplete quant;
- `EMPTY_DELIVERY_METHODS`: available delivery methods aren't found;

OrderCreateRequestV2DeliverySchemaEnum.description:
Delivery scheme:
- `MIX`: at Ozon choice;
- `FBO`: FBO;
- `FBS`: FBS.

DeliveryTypeEnum.description:
Delivery type:
- `COURIER`: by courier;
- `PVZ`: to pick-up point;
- `POSTAMAT`: to parcel terminal.
